<BR><DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c6"><SPAN CLASS="c7">TOP OF THE WORLD</SPAN></P>
</DIV>
<BR><DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c6"><SPAN CLASS="c8">BYLINE: </SPAN><SPAN CLASS="c2">The Hamilton Spectator</SPAN></P>
</DIV>
<BR><DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c6"><SPAN CLASS="c8">SECTION: </SPAN><SPAN CLASS="c2">CANADA/WORLD; Pg. A04</SPAN></P>
